### **2. Generator Options and Interface** (`packages/generator/src`)

**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775502840807-dsqnic/packages/generator/src`

