### **4. Prisma Scalar Types to TypeScript Mapping**

**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775502840807-dsqnic/packages/client-generator-ts/src/utils/common.ts`

```typescript
const GraphQLScalarToJSTypeTable = {
