### **6. DMMFHelper - The Working Interface**

**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775502840807-dsqnic/packages/client-generator-ts/src/dmmf.ts`

The `DMMFHelper` wraps DMMF.Document and provides convenient lookups:

```typescript
export class DMMFHelper implements DMMF.Document {
  constructor(public document: DMMF.Document) {}

  // Direct access to datamodel
  get datamodel(): DMMF.Datamodel { return this.document.datamodel }

  // Cached lookup maps
  get typeAndModelMap(): Dictionary<DMMF.Model> { /* models + types */ }
  get mappingsMap(): Dictionary<DMMF.ModelMapping> { /* operation mappings */ }
  get outputTypeMap(): NamespacedTypeMap<DMMF.OutputType> { /* schema types */ }
  get rootFieldMap(): Dictionary<DMMF.SchemaField> { /* root Query/Mutation */ }

  // Convenience methods
  isComposite(name: string): boolean
  hasEnumInNamespace(enumName: string, namespace: 'model' | 'prisma'): boolean
  resolveInputObjectType(ref: DMMF.InputTypeRef): DMMF.InputType | undefined
  resolveOutputObjectType(ref: DMMF.OutputTypeRef): DMMF.OutputType | undefined
  getOtherOperationNames(): string[]  // executeRaw, queryRaw, etc.
